# Components Used

## Hardware Components

| Component | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Arduino Uno | Main controller for PID computation |
| BTS7960 Motor Driver | High-current motor driving |
| N20 Encoder Motor | DC motor with rotational feedback |
| Breadboard | Signal routing and prototyping |
| 12V DC Adapter | Motor power supply |
| Jumper Wires | Electrical connections |
| 10kΩ Resistors | Encoder pull-up stabilization |
| 0.1µF Capacitor | Encoder noise filtering |
| 100µF Capacitor | Motor noise suppression |

## Software Used

- Arduino IDE
- Embedded C/C++
- Serial Monitor for debugging and tuning
